<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Web Development Course</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/web-development.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Web Development Course</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Learn how to create dynamic, responsive, and interactive websites</p>
  </header>

  <!-- Course Content -->
  <div class="course-details">
    <section class="course-introduction">
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>In this course, you'll master the fundamental and advanced aspects of web development, covering both front-end and back-end technologies. By the end of the course, you will be able to create full-stack web applications from scratch.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="course-modules">
      <h2>Course Modules</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Module 1:</strong> Introduction to HTML and CSS</li>
        <li><strong>Module 2:</strong> JavaScript Fundamentals</li>
        <li><strong>Module 3:</strong> Responsive Web Design with Bootstrap</li>
        <li><strong>Module 4:</strong> Advanced JavaScript Techniques</li>
        <li><strong>Module 5:</strong> Backend Development with Node.js</li>
        <li><strong>Module 6:</strong> Database Integration with MongoDB</li>
        <li><strong>Module 7:</strong> Project: Building a Full-Stack Application</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="course-outcomes">
      <h2>Learning Outcomes</h2>
      <p>By completing this course, you will:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Understand the structure and styling of web pages using HTML and CSS.</li>
        <li>Develop interactive and dynamic user experiences with JavaScript.</li>
        <li>Build responsive, mobile-friendly layouts using modern techniques.</li>
        <li>Develop and deploy server-side applications with Node.js and Express.</li>
        <li>Integrate and manage databases for data storage and retrieval.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="course-instructor">
      <h2>Meet the Instructor</h2>
      <div class="instructor-info">
        <img src="/Codding Icons.jpg" alt="Instructor's Photo" class="instructor-photo">
        <div class="instructor-details">
          <h3>John Doe</h3>
          <p>John is a seasoned web developer with over 10 years of experience in both front-end and back-end technologies. He has worked with leading tech companies and is passionate about sharing his knowledge with others.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="course-enrollment">
        <h2>Enroll Now</h2>
        <p>Ready to start your journey into web development? Enroll now and begin building your future.</p>
        <!-- Enroll Button -->
        <button class="enroll-btn" id="enrollBtn">Enroll Now</button>
    </section>
  </div>


</body>
</html>
